'''社交网络游戏'''，又稱為'''社群遊戲'''，是在线游戏的一种，它通过[[社交网络|社交网络]]游玩，通常使用[[多人游戏|多人]]与[[异步|异步]]游戏性机制<ref>[http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/4009/the_social_network_game_boom.php The Social Network Game Boom] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/4009/the_social_network_game_boom.php |date=20140623053750 }} by Sande Chen from ''[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]'' (April 29, 2009)</ref><ref>[http://radoff.com/blog/2010/05/24/history-social-games/ History of Social Games] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100527090108/http://radoff.com/blog/2010/05/24/history-social-games/ |date=2010-05-27 }} by Jon Radoff (May 24, 2010)</ref><ref>[http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1935113,00.html The Odd Popularity of Mafia Wars] {{Wayback|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1935113,00.html |date=20130826153003 }} by Lev Grossman from ''[[Time_(magazine)|TIME]]'' (Nov. 16, 2009)</ref><ref>[http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1935113,00.html Workshop: Game Design for Social Networks, Proceedings of the 13th International MindTrek Conference: Everyday Life in the Ubiquitous Era] {{Wayback|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1935113,00.html |date=20130826153003 }} by Aki Järvinen from ''[[Time_(magazine)|TIME]]'' (2009)</ref>。社交网络游戏多常以[[浏览器游戏|浏览器游戏]]形式实现，但也可以在移动设备等平台运作<ref>{{cite news|last=Kim|first=Ryan|title=The Future of Social Games is Mobile|url=http://gigaom.com/2010/10/12/the-future-of-social-games-is-mobile/|accessdate=2011-10-11|newspaper=Gigaom|date=2010-10-12|archive-date=2011-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111005150448/http://gigaom.com/2010/10/12/the-future-of-social-games-is-mobile/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第一个[[跨平台|跨平台]]“脸书到手机”社交游戏由[[芬兰|芬兰]]公司[[Star_Arcade|Star Arcade]]在2011年开发<ref>{{cite web|title=Star Arcade launches world’s first Facebook-to-Mobile multi player game|url=http://wirelessduniya.com/2012/02/15/star-arcade-launches-worlds-first-facebook-to-mobile-multi-player-game/|publisher=WirelessDuniya|accessdate=2014-03-24|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140709023218/http://wirelessduniya.com/2012/02/15/star-arcade-launches-worlds-first-facebook-to-mobile-multi-player-game/|archivedate=2014年7月9日|df=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=First Multi-player Game On Facebook|url=http://www.consumerlab.es/first-multi-player-game-on-facebook/|publisher=Consumer Lab / McCann Worldgroup|accessdate=2014-03-24|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140324111518/http://www.consumerlab.es/first-multi-player-game-on-facebook/|archivedate=2014-03-24}}</ref>。

社交网络游戏是全球最流行游戏的游戏之一，一些产品用户量达数千万<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/technology/8376392.stm "Social network games catch the eye of computer giants"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/technology/8376392.stm |date=20141027213245 }} by Zoe Kleinman from [[BBC_News|BBC News]] (Nov. 2009)</ref>。《[[(Lil)_Green_Patch|(Lil) Green Patch]]》、《[[开心农场|开心农场]]》<ref>{{cite news|last=Kohler|first=Chris|title=14. Happy Farm (2008)|url=http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2009/12/the-15-most-influential-games-of-the-decade/2/|work=The 15 Most Influential Games of the Decade|publisher=''[[Wired_(magazine){{!}}Wired|Wired (magazine){{!}}Wired]]''|accessdate=2011-09-10|date=2009-12-24|page=2|archive-date=2011-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111002143503/http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2009/12/the-15-most-influential-games-of-the-decade/2|dead-url=no}}</ref>、《[[农场小镇|农场小镇]]》、《[[YoVille|YoVille]]》和《[[黑帮战争|黑帮战争]]》是同类游戏中的佼佼者。《[[拓荒者小镇|拓荒者小镇]]》、《[[城市小镇|城市小镇]]》、《[[时光花园|时光花园]]》、《[[舰队收藏|舰队收藏]]》<ref>2013-10-10, [http://www.inside-games.jp/article/2013/10/10/71039.html 提督100万人突破、そして島田フミカネ氏による航空母艦も実装決定！ ─ 『艦これ』秋のイベントも実施準備中] {{Wayback|url=http://www.inside-games.jp/article/2013/10/10/71039.html |date=20140701113419 }}, インサイド</ref><ref>2013-11-14, [http://ascii.jp/elem/000/000/842/842194/ 艦これをパズドラと並べないでください] {{Wayback|url=http://ascii.jp/elem/000/000/842/842194/ |date=20131123202757 }}, ASCII.jp</ref>和《[[模拟时光|模拟时光]]》是近期热门社交游戏的例子{{citation needed|time=2014-07-11T13:59:47+00:00}}。

